column5: You lucky dog! Have a great trip up North. Keith is chomping at the bit already! Don't suppose you could take a littel exrta luggage and stuff Wayne in one and me in the other could ya?

Thanks Ron! It'd be great it if you and Wayne were joining us, too bad you couldnt make it. Apreciate the well wishes and we'll try not to let you down! Man I'm chomping at the bit.....  How was Rice yesterday?  Cheers
Have a safe and productive trip up north bud. Bring back the pictures so we can all gloat and be envious.    Art
A memorable trip to you, Dano. Have a great time!
Have fun my friend. Hope you and Keith get in to some Monsters!
have a great time  lots of pictures so we can live vicariously, through you and your pics
Thanks guys, I wish you were all coming with me!  Cheers
Careful on what you wish for Dano!
